<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/1223> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #1223" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cap., Degrassi 44f., 117, 438f." ;
	dprr:hasID 1223 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/1219> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #1219" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cap. (names entire); Plut. Numa 20.2; Eutrop. 3.3; Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Oros. 4.12.2; Cassiod.; and on Torquatus, Act. Tr.; Varro LL 5.165; Liv. 23.34.15; see Degrassi 44f., 117, 438f. Torquatus campaigned in Sardinia and celebrated a triumph (Act. Tr., Degrassi 76f., 549; Liv. 23.34.15; Per. 20; Vell. 2.38.2; Eutrop. 3.3; Oros. 4.12.2). On the closing of the temple of Ianus in this consulship, see Varro LL 5.165; Liv. 1.19.3; Vell. 2.38.3; Plut. Numa 20.2; Fort. Rom. 9; Eutrop. 3.3; Oros. 4.12.4; Schol. Veron. on Verg. Aen. 7.607." ;
	dprr:hasID 1219 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/1189> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #1189" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cap. (names entire); Flor. 1.18.30, on Buteo; Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod.; see Degrassi 42f., 116, 436f. Florus (1.18.30-32) speaks of a victory over the Punic fleet at Aegimurus, followed by storm and shipwreck, Zonaras (8.16) of the continued changes of command." ;
	dprr:hasID 1189 .
